<<<<<System requirements>>>>> Before running this container, ensure your system meets the following requirements.

        Apptainer / Singularity runtime
        Linux x86_64 architecture

        CPU-only — no GPU or GPU driver required

        Minimum 4GB RAM (8GB+ recommended; scale with dataset size)
        Minimum 10GB free disk space for container and cache

<<<<</System requirements>>>>>
========================================================================================
<<<<<Included Packages>>>>> The container ships with a classical machine learning and data science stack pre-installed, so most workflows work out of the box with no extra setup. This is a representative list of the core packages present across builds of this container family, not the full install — run a shell inside the container and use `pip list` to see everything actually installed in a given build.

        Machine Learning
        --------------------------------
        scikit-learn, xgboost, lightgbm, category-encoders

        Data Science & Visualization
        --------------------------------
        numpy, pandas, scipy, statsmodels, matplotlib, seaborn, plotly

        Development & Notebooks
        --------------------------------
        jupyterlab

<<<<</Included Packages>>>>>
